snippet.title: Wizard of Legend Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Wizard of Legend is a fast paced dungeon crawler with rogue-like elements where you assume the role of a powerful wizard on their quest for fame and glory!

Try the demo now on Kickstarter:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/contingent99/wizard-of-legend

Trailer Soundtrack by Dale North
https://www.youtube.com/user/DaleNorth
via Scarlet Moon Productions:
http://scarletmoonproductions.com/artists/
